column5: 🙋🏾‍♀️ my hubs wont hit my bong so, yes

I haven’t seen my friends in weeks. If it’s not via social media we probably haven’t seen of spoken and even then no one asks about me. I always have to move the conversation to myself because everyone always wants help with their drama and sometimes I just don’t want to take on additional bullshit.
I’ve been obsessing over moving for this reason 😑
Oh man, this plant hates me 😭 I gave up on them lol good luck to you!!
I have  a monstera leaf that turned up with a random burn looking mark smack in the middle and then decided to start yellowing as well :(  feel this in my soul
So pretty! I want to try this
